name: Cycle Tyre
description: rubber covering that fits around the rim of a bicycle wheel to provide traction, cushioning, and protection against punctures. It typically consists of a rubber tread that contacts the ground.

name: Cycle Seat
description: A cycle seat is designed to provide support and comfort to the rider during long rides. It can be made from a variety of materials such as leather, synthetic materials, or gel padding.

name: Cycle Gear
description: Cycle gear refers to the equipment and accessories worn or used by a cyclist for safety, comfort, and performance. This can include clothing, helmets, shoes, gloves, eyewear,locks, pumps, and tools.
